{"id":27662,"date":"2024-02-11T12:53:37","date_gmt":"2021-11-11T07:23:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=27662"},"modified":"2022-11-07T15:53:09","modified_gmt":"2022-11-07T10:23:09","slug":"types-of-wardrobe","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/types-of-wardrobe\/","title":{"rendered":"A Sneak Peek Into The Different Types Of Wardrobes For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>A perfect <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-design-for-bedroom\/\"><em>wardrobe design<\/em><\/a><em> can accommodate all your needs and requirements, complement the layout and theme of the bedroom both functionally and aesthetically, and also reflect your personality and style<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A modern wardrobe is no longer considered only a functional piece of furniture in the bedroom. We know they help keep your personal stuff and accessories in a neat and organised manner, but this personal space (read: wardrobe) has come a long way if we see it from an aesthetic perspective.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, the type of wardrobe design you choose isn\u2019t as simple as you think as you need to keep several factors in mind. Let\u2019s read ahead to find out what they are.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What Are The Different Types Of Bedroom Wardrobes That You Can Choose From?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some factors determine the type of bedroom wardrobe you choose. These are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>The bedroom\u2019s layout and total space available (~<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/how-to-choose-wardrobe-for-bedroom\/\">the height, width and depth of the wardrobe<\/a>)<\/li><li>The wardrobe\u2019s interior layout (number of drawers\/shelves\/hanging rods) and exterior layout (number of doors)<\/li><li>The wardrobe\u2019s structure (freestanding wardrobe, built-in wardrobe, wall-to-wall wardrobe, floor-to-ceiling wardrobe)<\/li><li>Your personal wardrobe style (wardrobe with mirror, wardrobe with attached study table\/make-up corner, etc.)<\/li><li>Type of wardrobe material (solid wood, veneer, MDF, transparent\/frosted glass, laminate, particleboard, plywood)<\/li><li>Kind of door opening mechanism (hinge door, swing door, no door, shutter door, folding door, sliding door)<\/li><li>The number of items and the types of articles you want to store<\/li><li>Load bearing and storage capacity<\/li><li>Your buying budget<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s our lowdown on the popular types of wardrobes for the bedroom for you to get inspired from. So, let\u2019s get to it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Angular Wooden Wardrobe That Looks Stunning<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This angular wooden wardrobe looks quite modern and stunning with its walnut finish. It is a perfect choice for those looking for a large storage space with multiple compartments and versatile drawers to store their wardrobe essentials. You will be able to access everything that you need easily without digging through the piles. This <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">wooden wardrobe design<\/a> also acts as a smart partition to separate the bedroom and the dressing corner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124040\/angular-wooden-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Angular wooden wardrobe is a different type of wardrobe, and it comes with ample storage space with multiple compartments\" class=\"wp-image-27663\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124040\/angular-wooden-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124040\/angular-wooden-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124040\/angular-wooden-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124040\/angular-wooden-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This angular wardrobe allows your accessories and clothes to breathe well<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Functional wardrobe designs for your modern bedroom!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/07152629\/functional-wardrobe-designs-for-your-modern-bedroom.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Concealed Wardrobes Are A Super Space Saver<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This concealed wardrobe is a super space saver as it is built into the wall and remains hidden as a part of the TV showcase when its doors are closed. The colour of the wardrobe also blends well with the light grey walls of the room, resulting in a soft look and feel for the bedroom. The wardrobe doors are hinged and swing open at a 90-degree angle, making it easy for you to gain a full view of the wardrobe\u2019s interiors and spot personal items conveniently.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124047\/concealed-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-bedroom-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Concealed wardrobe is a different type of bedroom wardrobe built into the wall with handles doors\" class=\"wp-image-27664\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124047\/concealed-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-bedroom-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124047\/concealed-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-bedroom-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124047\/concealed-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-bedroom-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124047\/concealed-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-bedroom-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Measure the dimensions of your wardrobe doors carefully when designing the wardrobe structure so that there is sufficient walking space around it<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Customised Two-Door Wardrobe For A Bold Statement<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This customised two-door wardrobe makes a luxurious and bold statement in this classic black and white-themed bedroom. It features a freestanding wardrobe with clear glass doors, and vertical storage shelves\/drawers attached on both ends making it a single and focal furniture piece in your bedroom. The provision of light within the wardrobe makes it easier for you to search for your clothes and related stuff easily even when the bedroom lights are dim at night.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124055\/customised-two-door-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"A customized two-door wardrobe is a type of wardrobe that features a freestanding closet with clear glass doors\" class=\"wp-image-27665\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124055\/customised-two-door-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124055\/customised-two-door-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124055\/customised-two-door-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124055\/customised-two-door-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>You can make efficient use of the wardrobe\u2019s roof as an extra storage space for your bags\/suitcases if your bedroom has a high ceiling<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Freestanding Wardrobe (His And Hers)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This freestanding wardrobe set features two separate <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/glass-wardrobe-design\/\">glass door wardrobes<\/a> to differentiate between his and hers. Alternatively, you can also use one wardrobe to organise clothes, jewellery, shoes and accessories and the other wardrobe to store bed sheets, pillows, quilts, etc.. The glass doors reflect the light in the bedroom and make it look more spacious and airier. The empty middle space between the wardrobes can be set up with a dressing table area with lights.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124100\/freestanding-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Freestanding wardrobe is a type of wardrobe furniture with two separate glass door wardrobes for his and hers\" class=\"wp-image-27666\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124100\/freestanding-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124100\/freestanding-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124100\/freestanding-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124100\/freestanding-wardrobe-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The two wardrobes and the dressing\/make-up area in the middle act as a visually appealing focal point for your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Laminate Wardrobe To Keep Up With The Trends<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wardrobe-laminate-design\/\">Laminate wardrobe designs<\/a> have become quite a popular alternative to solid wood bedroom wardrobes these days. Laminates not only provide more strength and protection as compared to hardwood but are environment-friendly too. There are different types of laminates for the wardrobe \u2014 decorative laminate (usage-based), matt finish and glossy-finish laminate (surface finish-based), high-pressure and low-pressure laminates (manufacturing-based.)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124106\/laminate-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"A laminate wardrobe is a different type of wardrobe that provides more strength and protection also environment-friendly\" class=\"wp-image-27667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124106\/laminate-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124106\/laminate-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124106\/laminate-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124106\/laminate-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Learn about the differences between laminates and veneers for wardrobe here<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Are you ready to make your wardrobe the show stopper of your bedroom\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16134425\/make-wardrobe-show-stopper-of-bedroom.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Walk-In Wardrobes For Ample Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a large space and a big budget to spare, this wooden walk-in wardrobe will be an ideal go-to option. It has a mix of open cabinets and closed cabinets with transparent sliding doors, which do not take up much room in front of them and do not hinder the flow of traffic in the room. Which type of wood is best for a wardrobe like this? It is BWP plywood as it is durable, strong and moisture-resistant.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124118\/walk-in-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"A walk-in wardrobe is a different type of wardrobe design with a mix of open and closed cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-27669\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124118\/walk-in-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124118\/walk-in-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124118\/walk-in-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124118\/walk-in-wardrobe-is-a-different-type-of-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>You can also spare some space in the walk-in wardrobe for a dressing\/make-up area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wide Wardrobe with Sliding Doors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This wide wardrobe with sliding doors is a modern and contemporary take on the classic and traditional hinge-door wardrobes. You can insert any number of sliding doors (say, 2-4) depending upon the width of the wardrobe. A walk-in wardrobe gives you extra space in the main bedroom for other furniture items. You can customise the wardrobe\u2019s interior layout depending upon your needs and requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124125\/wide-wardrobe-with-sliding-doors-is-a-type-of-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Wide wardrobe with sliding doors is a type of wardrobe that gives extra space in the main bedroom for other furniture items\" class=\"wp-image-27670\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124125\/wide-wardrobe-with-sliding-doors-is-a-type-of-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124125\/wide-wardrobe-with-sliding-doors-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124125\/wide-wardrobe-with-sliding-doors-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11124125\/wide-wardrobe-with-sliding-doors-is-a-type-of-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This dark grey wardrobe gives a smart, opulent and bold look and feel to this space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this blog post has equipped you with a good amount of knowledge about the types of wardrobes you can adorn your bedroom with. Let us know in the comment box below which wardrobes from the collection above did you like the most? Remember, the interior design team at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Design Cafe<\/a> is just a call away if you need more guidance on the same for your bedroom.<\/p>\n\r\n\